<paragraph id="24261152BC4AFFB6FF01FB00FD0822F8" blockId="10.[178,1085,1185,1266]" pageId="10" pageNumber="1145">E t y m o l o g y: The specific epithet (Latin, adjective: equal, similar) refers to the absence of a sexual dimorphism of the pronotum, one of the characters separating this species from most geographically close consubgeners.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="24261152BC4AFFB6FF01FAA0FED62358" blockId="10.[178,1085,1282,1362]" pageId="10" pageNumber="1145">
