<taxonomicName id="E3996AD1BC4AFFB6FCDFFAA0FC1A231D" authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2011" box="[876,970,1282,1303]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Geostiba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="1145" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aequa">
<emphasis id="16EDCD40BC4AFFB6FCDFFAA0FC1A231D" box="[876,970,1282,1303]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="1145">G. aequa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
would key out at couplets 96-98. In order to accommodate the new species, the key is modified as follows:
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="24261152BC4AFFB6FF01FA21FBED23D7" blockId="10.[178,1085,1411,1579]" pageId="10" pageNumber="1145">
