). Western (three species) and southern 
<collectingCountry id="5C8E51C2BC4AFFB6FE1EFA6AFDD023D7" box="[429,512,1480,1501]" name="Turkey" pageId="10" pageNumber="1145">Anatolia</collectingCountry>
